                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 178) I went and took the prisoner. He put his foot out, threw me down, and gave me several kicks on the face—I found on him 51/4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—the ham was worth 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I was very ill-used by him and others.</p>
